</li>
<li>
<p><strong>38.8 million Americans</strong> (13.6% of the population) use smart speakers for shopping tasks. (<a href="https://www.emarketer.com/content/smart-speaker-shopping-forecast">eMarketer</a>)</p>
</li>
<li>
